二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required TextsNone
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online ResourcesNews pieces selected by students


三、教學目標 Objectives


To stimulate interest in reading English through news pieces on a wide variety of news topics.　


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall DescriptionGoals: To stimulate reading though reading current events related to the learners area of interest.To provide information and insight as a basis for better conversation skills.To provide the practice of public speaking skills.Students are divided into groups of four. Each week one group member peer teaches the article to his/her group for the first fifty-minutes. During the second, class period, presenters give a summary of their news stories in turn to the whole class.Absences: Attendance is mandatory. Lateness is penalized.  Students are allowed to be absent three times without penalty. After that, the final score is reduced by ten points for each additional absence. Two “latenesses” equals one absence.

